title: Garlic-Herb Beef Rump & Brussels Sprouts with Roast Veggie Toss & Peppercorn Aioli
description: A crispy stack of colourful roasted veggies and Brussels sprouts create the base for a steak dish of joyous proportions. Tender
slices of beef rump are adorned in herby seasoning and topped by peppercorn aioli to take things up a notch. Now, if that
doesn't sound like heaven on earth, we don't know what does!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
